name: Santoro backpack with stroller THE DUET
description: Santoro school backpack with three compartments and built-in wheelchairs. The backpack features an ergonomically reinforced back and adjustable shoulder straps and a strap compartment when the backpack is not worn on the back, as well as a strong loop at the top for easy carrying and storage. It also contains two mesh partitions on the sides provided for a water bottle or umbrella. The backpack is closed with strong double-breasted zippers that contain a decorative pendant.

name: Backpack KIMMIDOLL
description: Large school backpack with two compartments and three pockets. The backpack contains two spacious compartments with a double zipper and one outer front pocket. On the sides of the backpack there is a stretchable pocket for a bottle or a small umbrella and one small pocket with a zipper. The backpack also contains a reinforced and softened back lined with mesh so as not to irritate the skin.

The pencil case is made of polyester and contains two spacious partitions and two strong zippers with a decorative pendant. Great choice for various accessories such as scissors, glue, concealer.
